<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="spot-n">spot <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /spɒt/    美 /spɑːt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>点；斑点；污点：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>ink spots
墨水渍</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My dog has some brown spots.
我的狗身上有一些褐色的斑点。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>地点；场所：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a scenic / <strong>beauty spot</strong>
风景胜地</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a historic spot
名胜古迹</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The most beautiful spot on the river is the Three Gorges.
长江最美丽的地方是三峡。</p><footer>外研④ – 5</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-the-spot">on the spot</h3>
<p>1.<strong>当场；在现场：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bullet struck his head and he was killed on the spot.
子弹击中了他的头部，他当场死亡。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police were on the spot within a few minutes.
几分钟内警察就赶到了现场。</p></div></div>